item.title: Ranking Star Wars Characters
item.description: .This all started because of a very contentious debate about the attractiveness of various Star Wars characters. I decided to use the Star Wars dataset to settle things once and for all. I cleaned up the dataset, so that it just contained the male characters and what I thought were important descriptors, like species, hair, and eye color. I also added a column for rank, so that my friends could fill out their own copies.
